led/button/fan control
----------------------
Python script to allow following functionalities:
1. allow the led (Dflt socket Grove shield D3) to blink
2. react with led blink (I2C socket 1)  timeback to start a shell script e.g. poweroff or wifi reconfigure.
3. control a relay (Dflt Grove shield D2) to control e.g. a fan (On/Off).

Use this in a shell script. Try `python MyLed.py --help` for command line usage.
